
Readme

#Requirements

docker
docker compose
Linux

#usage

first compose the dockerfile using the following command
sudo docker-compose up --build

The ports allocations are as follows
subscriber listens on port 5502,4402
publisher listens on port 5500,4400
docker is exposed on ports 5502,5500,4400,4402

open a browser on localhost port 4402,5502 for subscriber and 4400,5500 for publishers

publisher

select your publisher and topic --> write the article in the provided textarea --> click submit article to publish.

subscriber

select your subscriber then select the topic that you want to subscribe and click on the subscribe button.
click on the view subscriptions to view the articles that have been subscribed and published.

